                            <comment id="223935" author="jgmitter" created="Mon, 19 Mar 2018 13:03:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10825&quot; title=&quot;Configuring multi-rail with a large number of nodes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10825&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10825&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is opened for the MR configuration question.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="223933" author="jgmitter" created="Mon, 19 Mar 2018 12:58:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You are correct in that Dynamic Discovery is NOT present in 2.10.X and will be available with 2.11.X.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am going to move your bigger question about how to configure MR with a large number of nodes without DD to an LU ticket so that one of our LNet engineers can respond.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="223924" author="wutz" created="Mon, 19 Mar 2018 06:13:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Recently, wo prepare to deployment a lustre with multi-rail, but i don&apos;t known how to enable dynamic discovery.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We use lustre-2.10.3, it seems dynamic discovery is implementd in version 2.11.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have about 2 mgs/mds, 6 oss and 512 client nodes, how to configure static multi-rail with a large number of nodes ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
